## Getting Started

1. Clone the repo.

```bash
$ git clone https://YOUR-USERNAME@bitbucket.org/asperii/google-maps-danel.git
```

2. Go into the repository

```bash
  $ cd google-maps-danel
```

3. Install dependencies

```bash
  $ yarn install
  ## Or NPM
  $ npm install
```

4. Run your local build. This step opens your web browser and navigates to http://localhost:3000/.

```bash
  $ yarn start
  ## Or NPM
  $ npm start
```
